data.description: Welcome to this fully updated home featuring vaulted ceilings and an in-house speaker system. The open-concept living area flows seamlessly to a fully fenced backyard with a spacious deck, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The modern kitchen showcases quartz counters, and a cozy fireplace in the living room provides a warm atmosphere for chilly evenings. This property also offers a detached garage for convenient parking and storage. Enjoy the perfect blend of contemporary living and comfort in this inviting home. - Schedule a showing now!
